Com. vs. Peter Plowden. Assault and Battery. Martin Hoover, Prosecutor.
                        Verdict, guilty. Sentenced to pay costs. Sharpe and Stenger for Com.;
                        McGowan for Deft.

Com. vs. Frederick Myers. Surety of the Peace. Margaret Kyle, Prosecutrix.
                        Complaint dismissed. Deft. to pay costs. Stenger and Kimmell for Com.;
                        McCauley and Orr for Deft.

Com. vs. Charles Jones. Assault and Battery on Peter Dorte, Prosecutor.
                        Verdict, guilty. Sentenced to pay costs. Stenger and Kimmell for Com.;
                        Douglas for Deft.

Com. vs. Jacob Hite. Surety of Peace. Adam Vanderan, Prosecutor.
                        Dismissed--each party to pay his own costs. Stenger and Kimmell for Com.;
                        Brewer for Deft.

Com. vs. Thomas Morgan. Assault and Battery. Eveline Howard,
                        Prosecutrix.--Verdict, guilty. Sentenced to pay costs,--Stenger for Com.;
                        Kimmell for Deft.
